title: We are rich in natural beauty!
posting_body: ['Text ID # 1610C to my cell for more info!', 'Experience vibrant living at The Apartments, surrounded by rich culture and natural beauty that only Austin has to offer.', 'If you crave connected living – to your neighborhood, to your community, to business hubs with shopping, dining and recreation, along with stunning views of the downtown Austin Skyline, choose The Mont!', 'Elevated by premium interior finishes and community spaces that promote convenience, wellness and relaxation, you’ll see for yourself why you’ll love living here.', 'Perfectly located in the East Riverside Corridor ten minutes outside of Downtown Austin, you’re never far from where you need to be.', 'Whether you commute 3 miles to the new Oracle campus or 6 miles to Tesla’s new headquarters, your drive in will be a breeze.', 'Last minute work trips or quick getaways won’t even stress you out before takeoff since you’re only five miles from the airport terminal.', "You can discover new favorite bands at Emo’s Austin Music Venue or play some classic records on the Jukebox at Frazier's Long & Low, just off of East Riverside Drive.", 'Be sure to venture out a couple miles and get back to nature enjoying a paddleboard or kayaking excursion at Lady Bird Lake.', 'You can even enjoy the water just hitting some golf balls at the Riverside Golf Course in Roy Guerrero Park.', 'Life is extraordinary– how you live it should be too!', 'Choose The Apartments in Austin, TX and experience luxury and recreation like no other.', 'Call or stop by for a personalized tour of our community today.', 'Responsive image', 'Amenities', 'When you become a resident at The M in Austin, TX, you gain access to our noteworthy community amenities.', 'Lay out in the sun at our resort inspired pool featuring an inviting tanning deck.', 'Step up your fitness at our state of the art fitness center equipped with cardio machines, free weights and an open yoga studio.', 'In addition to our beautiful outdoor spaces, The Mont is environmentally conscious, offering residents access to onsite car charging stations, a community garden and so much more.', 'Don’t forget your four-legged friend!', 'The Mont will be their favorite place to explore.', 'Discover all of the ways you’ll love to spend your time at The M.', 'Resort Inspired Pool & Tanning Deck', 'Car Charging Station', 'WiFi Enabled Amenity Spaces', 'State of the Art Fitness Center', 'Cardio & Free Weight Studio', 'Open Yoga Studio', 'Resident Business Center']
